dct_title_s: A complete map of the Feather & Yuba rivers
dct_description_sm: compiled from the recent surveys of M. Milleson & R. Adams, C. Engineers ; Lith Justh & Co. Brodway St. S.F.
Coordiantes approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, waterways, cities and towns, ranches, diggings, routes.
"Respectfully dedicated to the Yankee Nation by the Publisher."
"Entered according to act of Congress in June A 1851 by R.A. Eddy, in the Clerks office of the District Court for the Northern District of California. "
Pictorial vignette of street in Marysville (including Marysville Bookstore) / drawn by M. Milleson.
